main event: A UFO was observed hovering for 2 minutes at Kunsan AB, Korea. It was described as round and bright by pilots returning from a mission. The conclusion was that it was probably an aircraft due to insufficient data for evaluation.
interesting points: The UFO was observed by pilots returning from a mission at Kunsan AB, Korea.
The object was described as round and bright.
The report mentions insufficient data for evaluation and concludes it was probably an aircraft.
The duration of the observation was 2 minutes.
There were no photographs present in the document.
